@node Keys "Keys"
You can quickly perform many operations by using one of Helm's key
commands. In most instances, you press a single key. Sometimes, you have
to hold down a qualifier key as you press the key. The qualifier keys
are shift, control, and ALT.

   1.   @{" Navigation " link KeysNavigation}
   2.   @{" Painting " link KeysPainting}
   3.   @{" Drawing " link KeysDrawing}
   4.   @{" Text Editing " link KeysText}
@endnode

@node KeysNavigation "Navigation Keys"
Use these keys to browse through a book. You can use the keys at any
time. The cursor keys will not work if you have selected an object
with one of the draw tools.

q	Quit
Return	Point
